MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

In re Report of the Commission on Continuing Legal Education Charles Edward Clendenin (# 0016609), Respondent.

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration of this court’s order of January 27, 2003, be, and hereby is, denied. For earlier order, see 98 Ohio St.3d 1426, 2003-Ohio-318, 782 N.E.2d 583.
